'From Squeak3.2gamma of 15 January 2002 [latest update: #4743] on 3 March 2002 at 3:45:43 pm'!"Change Set:		scrollBarAgain-dewDate:			3 March 2002Author:			Doug WayReverts the 4722fixScrollbarOnRight update, since that caused problems with morph lists being reordered and windows coming to front when they shouldn't.  This reimplements support for displaying flop-out scrollbars on the right by reordering the pane morphs in the SystemWindow, during window creation."!!ScrollPane methodsFor: 'scrolling' stamp: 'RAA 12/18/2000 17:15'!showScrollBar	(submorphs includes: scrollBar) ifTrue: [^ self].	self resizeScrollBar.	self privateAddMorph: scrollBar atIndex: 1.	"scrollBar changed."	retractableScrollBar ifFalse: [self resetExtent]! !!SystemWindow methodsFor: 'panes' stamp: 'dew 3/3/2002 12:36'!addMorph: aMorph fullFrame: aLayoutFrame	super addMorph: aMorph fullFrame: aLayoutFrame.	paneMorphs _ paneMorphs copyReplaceFrom: 1 to: 0 with: (Array with: aMorph).	Preferences alternativeWindowLook		ifFalse:			[aMorph borderWidth: 1.			aMorph color: self paneColor]		ifTrue:			[aMorph adoptPaneColor: self paneColor.			aMorph borderWidth: 2; borderColor: #inset; color: Color transparent].	Preferences scrollBarsOnRight	"reorder panes so flop-out right-side scrollbar is visible"		ifTrue: [self addMorphBack: aMorph]! !